Available Tools: select_records | select_with_filter | select_with_join | count_records
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "table": "string", "columns": ["string"], "where": "string", "limit": number }
Response Schema: { "rows": [{}], "count": number, "query_ms": number }
---
Question: Join employees and departments to list employee names and department titles for the first 8 staff members.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "employees", "columns": ["employees.full_name", "departments.title"], "where": "employees.dept_id = departments.id", "limit": 8 }
Response: { "rows": [{"full_name": "John Doe", "title": "Engineering"}, {"full_name": "Jane Roe", "title": "Marketing"}, {"full_name": "Sam Wilson", "title": "Sales"}, {"full_name": "Lisa Ray", "title": "HR"}, {"full_name": "Tom Hardy", "title": "Finance"}, {"full_name": "Amy Pond", "title": "Legal"}, {"full_name": "Ben Stark", "title": "Operations"}, {"full_name": "Clara Oswald", "title": "Support"}], "count": 8, "query_ms": 14 }
