Question: Join bookings and rooms to retrieve room numbers and guest names for booking ID 5099.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "bookings", "columns": ["rooms.room_number", "guests.guest_name"], "where": "bookings.room_id = rooms.id AND bookings.guest_id = guests.id AND bookings.id = 5099", "limit": 10 }
Response: { "rows": [{"room_number": "304", "guest_name": "Maria Garcia"}, {"room_number": "304", "guest_name": "Carlos Garcia"}], "count": 2, "query_ms": 21 }
