Question: Select customer names and their total reservation cost by joining customers, bookings, and payments, limited to the top 5 highest spenders.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "customers", "columns": ["customers.name", "SUM(payments.amount) as total_cost"], "where": "customers.id = bookings.customer_id AND bookings.id = payments.booking_id", "limit": 5 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "Robert Chen", "total_cost": 4500.00}, {"name": "Emily Davis", "total_cost": 3200.50}, {"name": "David Kim", "total_cost": 2950.75}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 38 }
