Question: Retrieve article titles and author names by joining articles and authors for posts published in 2024.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "articles", "columns": ["articles.title", "authors.name"], "where": "articles.author_id = authors.id AND articles.publish_date >= '2024-01-01'", "limit": 15 }
Response: { "rows": [{"title": "Future of AI", "name": "Dr. Alan Turing"}, {"title": "Quantum Computing", "name": "Marie Curie"}, {"title": "Green Energy", "name": "Elon Musk"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 19 }
