Question: List clinic names and doctor specialties by joining clinics and doctors where the clinic is located in 'New York'.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "clinics", "columns": ["clinics.name", "doctors.specialty"], "where": "clinics.id = doctors.clinic_id AND clinics.city = 'New York'", "limit": 30 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "Metro Health", "specialty": "Cardiology"}, {"name": "City Care", "specialty": "Pediatrics"}, {"name": "East Side Med", "specialty": "Neurology"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 17 }
